  "text": "In an attempt to deeper analyze the agri-food system it has been broken down into primary sector on the one hand and food industry on the other. The rest of the sectors of the VC have been grouped according to the technological classification used by [CITATION_1] 3 which identifies the following groups of industries: Energy, Materials, Traditional, Scale-intensive, Science-based, Specialized-suppliers, and Services (the industries included in each group are shown in the Supplementary Table 2 (pdf)). Results are shown in Table 2 .",
